  "index.48": { "zh": "从游艇研发设计、船厂制造监造，到交付后的运营管理、维修保养、保险合规——我们提供游艇全生命周期的一站式解决方案。", "en": "From yacht R&D design, shipyard manufacturing supervision, to post-delivery operation management, maintenance, insurance & compliance — we provide one-stop solutions for the entire yacht lifecycle." },
  "index.49": { "zh": "了解更多 →", "en": "Learn More →" },
