  "index.162": { "zh": "中东王室委托，历时38个月，搭载直升机平台、潜艇车库、IMAX影院。2024年荣获Asia Boating Awards年度最佳定制游艇。", "en": "Commissioned by Middle East royal family, 38 months in build, featuring helipad, submarine garage, IMAX theater. Winner of Asia Boating Awards 2024 Custom Yacht of the Year." },
