  "about.40": { "zh": "奇幻假期实业有限公司深耕高端游艇行业15年，为200+全球高净值客户提供游艇定制、租赁、托管全产业链一站式服务。", "en": "Fantastic Vacation Industrial Co., Ltd. has been deeply engaged in the high-end yacht industry for 15 years, providing 200+ global high-net-worth clients with one-stop services across the entire yacht industry chain: customization, charter, and management." },
